# Legacy API Integration

H5 reimplements **beeantmobile-main** (Ionic/Angular). TypeScript DTOs are hints only — **Legacy `req.Data` is the source of truth**.

## Before coding

1. Locate the Method in Legacy (e.g. `ApiMemberUrl-Passenger-Add`, `TmcApiHomeUrl-Staff-List`).
2. Trace `member.service.ts` / `tmc.service.ts` / `*-select-passenger*.base.page.ts` for the exact payload.
3. Document required fields, defaults, and date/enum formats in a short table (or PR note).
4. Compare with `packages/api/src/apis/<domain>.ts` — add **normalize** for response shape drift.

Do **not** infer fields from `shared-types` names alone (`CredentialNo` vs `Number`, `{ Staffs }` vs array in `Data`).

## Implementation pattern

```
Legacy req.Data  →  toXxxApiPayload()  →  proxy.send({ data })
Legacy response  →  normalizeXxxResponse() in apis/*.ts  →  hooks/UI
```

- Payload builders live next to the feature (`apps/h5/src/lib/*-form.ts`) or in `packages/api` when shared.
- **Mock handlers must accept the same payload** as real API (same field names/defaults).
- Strip UI-only fields; never send `StaffId` on external passenger APIs.

## Known Legacy shapes

| Pattern | Legacy | Wrong assumption |
|---------|--------|------------------|
| List APIs | `Data: T[]` | `Data: { Items: T[] }` |
| Staff-List | `StaffEntity[]` | `{ Staffs, TotalCount }` only |
| Passenger-List | `PassengerEntity[]` | `MemberPassenger` with `CredentialNo` |
| Passenger-Add (noEm) | `MemberCredential` spread (`Type`, `showCountry`, `isAdd`, no `PassengerType`) | extra `PassengerType` / wrong URL (`/Home/Proxy` vs `member-api/Passenger/Add`) |
| Proxy RPC | `Domain=rtesp.com`, `Language=cn`, direct service URL when Setting loaded | missing Domain; `zh-CN`; always `/Home/Proxy` |
| Dates | often `YYYY/MM/DD`; id-card expiry default `2100/01/01` | raw `type="date"` `YYYY-MM-DD` only |

## Branching (passenger / credentials)

| Scenario | Method family | Notes |
|----------|---------------|--------|
| 非公司员工 | `Passenger-Add/Modify/Remove` | stricter Mobile validation |
| 员工其他证件 | `Credentials-*` + `StaffId`, `IsRyx: true` | not Passenger-* |
| 我的证件 | `Credentials-*` (no StaffId) | Phase 4 `/me/credentials` |

## Delivery checklist

- [ ] Legacy Method + sample `req.Data` cited (file path or doc)
- [ ] `normalize*Response` if `Data` shape differs from DTO
- [ ] `to*ApiPayload()` for writes; mock uses identical shape
- [ ] `pnpm typecheck` passes; proxy + mock smoke path noted

## When reporting bugs

Include: **error message**, **Method name**, **request body**, **Legacy reference function**. Prefer fixing payload adapter over patching UI only.
